- Who is going to be the end-user of the software?
Mainly Assessors and sometimes Insurance consultants.

- How will they use it?
It must be web base so that they can access it from anywhere on their laptops
or tablets.

- What will be the input and output of the system?
The input:
Insurances Company detail
Insurance Consultants detail
Insurance Assessors detail
Claims/Cases detail
Client detail
Upload documents to specific insurance claims.

The output:
Display documents
Display comments on documents

Bonus output:
Send sms to client
Web call client to log call history
Add API endpoint

- What problem will it solve?
They need an application where they can manage the documents allocated to a
specific insurance claim by assessors and allow Insurance consultants to
view only the documents and add comments.
